o Collect Failures and document for user help

  1. ERROR [receive.c:202]: setsockopt (IP_ADD_MEMBERSHIP) failed (No such device)

     a) No kernel support
     b) No route (sudo ip r add 244.0.0.0/8 dev eth0)

